name: Ubume
skill: Deals 801/981 DMG to all enemies. Targets take 15%/19% more DMG for a limited time.

additional_data.description: The spirit of a mythological Chinese beast that captured humans. Now that she's a spirit, she stopped kidnapping people altogether. Instead, she just puts them in an altered state where they gain supernatural powers of concentration and don't respond to anything around them. As the effect gets more extreme, so does the look on her face. Needless to say, most people keep their distance from her when she's using her powers.

main: "Kidnapping?! I'd never do such a thing! I was just thinking about it, that's all!"
skill: "All of you! You're all my little babies!"
summon: "I'll do anything you need! Cooking, cleaning, kidnapping- anything!"
limit_break: "All my little babies are gone... Ah! They've come back!"
